<h2>Discover Brentwood Homes For Sale</h2>
<p>The community of Brentwood in Northwest Calgary consists of many mid-sized homes in a variety of Mid-Century styles. These homes line wide and inviting streets, shaded beneath tall, mature trees. Two large shopping centers, proximity to the downtown area, and Nose Hill Park are just some of the highlights in this family-friendly neighborhood.</p>
